            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px]"> Product liability issues arise when defective or unsafe products result in financial loss, injury, or harm to consumers. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We handle claims against manufacturers, sellers, and service providers, helping clients seek compensation and ensure responsibility for product defects or safety failures. </p>
         </div>
